OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan convicted of ambush    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshooting in New Mexico     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An Afghan refugee has been convicted of
OL,6, murder in one of three fatal           
OL,7, ambush-style shootings of Muslim men in
OL,8, the US state of New Mexico two years   
OL,9, ago.                                   
OL,11,FMuhammad Syed faces life in prison for 
OL,12,Fkilling 41-year-old Aftab Hussein on 26
OL,13,FJuly 2022. He still faces trial for the
OL,14,Fother two killings.                    
OL,16,FThe three victims were each found      
OL,17,Fgunned down in Albuquerque within the  
OL,18,Fspan of a few weeks.                   
OL,20,FThe murders caused widespread fear     
OL,21,Fwithin the city's Muslim community.    
